1
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[Preview]
Previously on Shrouding the Heavens,

2
00:00:10,083 --> 00:00:12,457
with the full support of the Yin-Yang Sect,

3
00:00:12,625 --> 00:00:14,416
Ye Fan successfully passed the entrance exam

4
00:00:14,500 --> 00:00:15,957
for the Immortal Platform Realm graduate program,

5
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:17,457
overseen by the three Grand Elders.

6
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:20,541
Meanwhile, Ji Ziyue revealed her secret technique

7
00:00:20,542 --> 00:00:22,166
for refining Primordial Qi Oil,

8
00:00:22,458 --> 00:00:24,499
which prompted Vice Principal Ji Daoyi—

9
00:00:24,583 --> 00:00:25,666
ranked eighth in the clan—

10
00:00:25,750 --> 00:00:28,874
to force an arranged meeting between her
and the reigning champion, Wang Teng.

11
00:00:29,708 --> 00:00:30,416
Since Wang Teng

12
00:00:30,417 --> 00:00:33,582
activated the Eternal Blue Gold
containing the Void Emperor's blood,

13
00:00:34,208 --> 00:00:36,249
the Ji family believed he was divinely favored.

14
00:00:36,417 --> 00:00:39,749
Wang Teng himself thought victory was assured.

15
00:00:40,083 --> 00:00:40,874
He decided

16
00:00:40,958 --> 00:00:42,832
to force the marriage with Ji Ziyue.

17
00:00:43,167 --> 00:00:44,041
But Ye Fan arrived

18
00:00:44,042 --> 00:00:46,832
just in time, like a rocket slicing through the sky.

19
00:00:47,417 --> 00:00:49,957
Amidst the roaring cheers of the audience,

20
00:00:50,125 --> 00:00:51,914
chanting "How about it? What can you do?"

21
00:00:52,458 --> 00:00:55,041
the battle for the title of
Strongest Graduate began.

22
00:00:55,750 --> 00:00:58,041
After an epic, rage-fueled probing attack,

23
00:00:58,167 --> 00:00:59,332
Wang Teng unleashed his ultimate technique:

24
00:00:59,375 --> 00:00:59,791
the Chaos Ancient Art's

25
00:00:59,833 --> 00:01:00,666
Eternal Banishment.

26
00:01:00,667 --> 00:01:01,667
However, Ye Fan countered

27
00:01:01,792 --> 00:01:02,332
using the Sun Scripture

28
00:01:02,333 --> 00:01:03,582
and the Bronze Coffin Sutra,

29
00:01:03,583 --> 00:01:04,041
breaking the attack completely.

30
00:01:04,042 --> 00:01:06,124
Thus, Wang Teng chose to perform
the "Slay Self, Illuminate Dao"

31
00:01:06,667 --> 00:01:07,749
ritual to ascend to the PhD level.

32
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:09,082
He published his thesis on the evolution

33
00:01:09,125 --> 00:01:10,457
of the Chaos Ancient Secret Art

34
00:01:10,833 --> 00:01:12,249
under the influence of the Front Word Secret.

35
00:01:12,250 --> 00:01:14,832
Unfortunately, his philosophy clashed
with his mentor, Elder Lun Gu.

36
00:01:15,333 --> 00:01:15,874
Consequently,

37
00:01:16,042 --> 00:01:19,082
Ye Fan—who had mastered the Four Secrets—

38
00:01:19,250 --> 00:01:20,957
found critical flaws in his logic,

39
00:01:21,042 --> 00:01:21,582
resulting in Wang Teng's thesis being rejected.

40
00:01:21,583 --> 00:01:23,124
Furthermore, Vice Principal Ji,

41
00:01:23,875 --> 00:01:25,541
who supported Wang Teng,

42
00:01:25,625 --> 00:01:27,582
was arrested for abusing public office.

43
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:28,624
And so,

44
00:01:28,708 --> 00:01:32,041
Ye Fan's battle against Wang Teng
to save Ziyue came to an end.

45
00:01:32,167 --> 00:01:33,291
This concludes last week's recap.

46
00:01:34,083 --> 00:01:36,332
Now, let us proceed to this week's events.

47
00:01:48,458 --> 00:01:49,458
Earth.

48
00:01:49,833 --> 00:01:50,374
Brother Ye,

49
00:01:50,458 --> 00:01:51,082
Pang Bo.

50
00:01:51,250 --> 00:01:52,999
So you two aren't from the Big Dipper Star?

51
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:54,541
Finally...

52
00:01:54,583 --> 00:01:55,791
It's been ten years.

53
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,000
Ye Zi...

54
00:01:57,458 --> 00:01:58,666
I can finally say it out loud.

55
00:01:58,792 --> 00:01:59,792
I was suffocating!

56
00:02:00,042 --> 00:02:02,582
No wonder you were so eager to befriend me.

57
00:02:02,833 --> 00:02:04,416
It was because of my unparalleled

58
00:02:04,417 --> 00:02:06,749
Void Crossing Technique, wasn't it?

59
00:02:06,750 --> 00:02:07,374
You...

60
00:02:07,583 --> 00:02:08,166
Dead dog,

61
00:02:08,458 --> 00:02:09,541
go screw yourself!

62
00:02:09,750 --> 00:02:11,041
Your unreliable teleportation

63
00:02:11,042 --> 00:02:12,582
sent me straight to the Central Plains.

64
00:02:12,833 --> 00:02:13,541
And Tu Fei...

65
00:02:13,625 --> 00:02:14,499
who knows where he's stuck,

66
00:02:14,500 --> 00:02:17,082
digging through some frozen wasteland in the North Plain.

67
00:02:17,542 --> 00:02:18,541
Today, my sister

68
00:02:18,542 --> 00:02:19,999
was able to break the engagement with Wang Teng

69
00:02:20,417 --> 00:02:21,749
all thanks to Brother Ye's aid.

70
00:02:22,542 --> 00:02:23,791
Haoyue is deeply grateful.

71
00:02:26,167 --> 00:02:27,167
However...

72
00:02:27,667 --> 00:02:28,667
my sister...

73
00:02:30,583 --> 00:02:31,583
If Brother Ye has no intention,

74
00:02:32,208 --> 00:02:33,208
please do not give her

75
00:02:34,333 --> 00:02:35,749
false hope that leads to obsession.

76
00:02:44,833 --> 00:02:46,916
Little Moon, who's usually so lively,

77
00:02:46,917 --> 00:02:48,082
why are you alone out here?

78
00:02:50,458 --> 00:02:50,791
[Wind blowing]

79
00:02:50,792 --> 00:02:52,499
Even the moon has its phases.

80
00:02:55,083 --> 00:02:55,666
True.

81
00:02:58,375 --> 00:02:59,375
Ziyue.

82
00:02:59,792 --> 00:03:00,792
Did you know,

83
00:03:01,125 --> 00:03:02,332
in my hometown,

84
00:03:03,125 --> 00:03:04,291
people often gaze at the moon

85
00:03:04,583 --> 00:03:06,707
to send thoughts to distant loved ones?

86
00:03:07,833 --> 00:03:08,249
The moon

87
00:03:09,042 --> 00:03:10,416
is a boat drifting in the heart,

88
00:03:11,083 --> 00:03:12,083
carrying the sorrow

89
00:03:12,458 --> 00:03:13,416
of separation.

90
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:16,000
Ziyue...

91
00:03:16,500 --> 00:03:17,500
Have you ever considered

92
00:03:18,333 --> 00:03:19,624
that beyond this vast land

93
00:03:19,792 --> 00:03:20,832
and endless cosmos,

94
00:03:21,833 --> 00:03:22,833
perhaps...

95
00:03:23,917 --> 00:03:25,082
this isn't the only realm?

96
00:03:26,667 --> 00:03:28,082
Are you saying

97
00:03:28,458 --> 00:03:30,041
you're not from this world?

98
00:03:31,083 --> 00:03:32,707
Then where exactly did you come from?

99
00:03:33,208 --> 00:03:34,208
Could it be...

100
00:03:34,625 --> 00:03:36,166
the legendary Immortal Domain?

101
00:03:42,792 --> 00:03:43,916
Look at that starry sky.

102
00:03:44,542 --> 00:03:45,582
Pang Bo and I

103
00:03:46,417 --> 00:03:47,417
came from the other side,

104
00:03:49,375 --> 00:03:50,791
from a place
incredibly far away.

105
00:03:51,208 --> 00:03:53,332
A world called Earth.

106
00:03:54,583 --> 00:03:55,583
No wonder...

107
00:03:59,333 --> 00:04:00,333
That explains why,

108
00:04:01,458 --> 00:04:03,291
for the past ten years,

109
00:04:03,292 --> 00:04:04,916
you never aligned with any faction

110
00:04:05,458 --> 00:04:07,374
and kept everyone at a distance.

111
00:04:10,375 --> 00:04:11,375
But these past ten years,

112
00:04:11,667 --> 00:04:12,916
I haven't been truly alone.

113
00:04:14,333 --> 00:04:15,207
There was the Black Emperor,

114
00:04:15,208 --> 00:04:16,082
the Holy Ape,

115
00:04:16,167 --> 00:04:17,167
and Heishui.

116
00:04:17,500 --> 00:04:18,500
What about me?

117
00:04:24,333 --> 00:04:25,416
You and them...

118
00:04:26,167 --> 00:04:27,167
are different.

119
00:04:27,625 --> 00:04:28,625
Different how?

120
00:04:32,125 --> 00:04:33,125
These ten years,

121
00:04:33,958 --> 00:04:35,082
I've traversed the stars

122
00:04:35,125 --> 00:04:36,125
and scoured ancient methods,

123
00:04:37,292 --> 00:04:38,999
all to reunite with my parents.

124
00:04:40,625 --> 00:04:42,249
But I knew that one day,

125
00:04:43,500 --> 00:04:45,249
I would have to say goodbye
to everything here.

126
00:04:49,292 --> 00:04:50,292
Yet, facing you...

127
00:04:56,542 --> 00:04:57,542
on that day of parting,

128
00:04:59,417 --> 00:05:00,832
I wouldn't know how to.

129
00:05:00,833 --> 00:05:02,332
If you already planned to leave,

130
00:05:02,958 --> 00:05:04,291
why risk everything

131
00:05:04,458 --> 00:05:06,207
to come to the Ji family
and break my engagement?

132
00:05:08,750 --> 00:05:10,499
Because at least when I leave,

133
00:05:11,542 --> 00:05:13,082
I want you to have the freedom

134
00:05:13,250 --> 00:05:14,832
to choose your own destiny.

135
00:05:27,917 --> 00:05:30,082
Crossing the starry domain
is no simple feat.

136
00:05:30,875 --> 00:05:32,457
To repay your kindness today,

137
00:05:33,083 --> 00:05:34,083
this Little Immortal

138
00:05:34,167 --> 00:05:36,041
will accompany you across
every corner of the Big Dipper.

139
00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:38,457
I swear I'll help you find a way home.

140
00:05:40,042 --> 00:05:41,624
And if we can't find a way...

141
00:05:41,625 --> 00:05:42,625
then I'll just

142
00:05:42,708 --> 00:05:43,749
create a new "Star Trampling Art"

143
00:05:43,792 --> 00:05:46,332
or something to get you back.

144
00:05:47,083 --> 00:05:48,083
It's a deal.

145
00:05:52,083 --> 00:05:53,582
Then tell me more about

146
00:05:53,792 --> 00:05:55,499
what interesting things exist
on Earth.

147
00:05:55,750 --> 00:05:56,750
Sure.

148
00:05:57,083 --> 00:05:58,166
On Earth,

149
00:05:58,333 --> 00:05:59,333
humans are mortals.

150
00:05:59,667 --> 00:06:01,082
Their lifespan is but a few decades.

151
00:06:01,583 --> 00:06:02,583
They can't fly either;

152
00:06:02,958 --> 00:06:04,582
they travel using vehicles

153
00:06:04,583 --> 00:06:05,791
called airplanes.

154
00:06:05,815 --> 00:06:30,915
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

155
00:06:31,125 --> 00:06:31,957
Xiao Nannan,

156
00:06:32,125 --> 00:06:33,125
come inside.

157
00:06:34,625 --> 00:06:36,457
That bronze coffin was what
withstood the Ji family's

158
00:06:36,750 --> 00:06:38,457
Void Ancient Mirror head-on.

159
00:06:38,792 --> 00:06:40,207
It's clearly no ordinary object.

160
00:06:40,667 --> 00:06:41,499
This bronze coffin

161
00:06:41,667 --> 00:06:42,791
shares a deep connection with me.

162
00:06:43,917 --> 00:06:45,374
If I can uncover its secrets,

163
00:06:46,625 --> 00:06:47,625
perhaps I can solve

164
00:06:48,083 --> 00:06:50,041
one of the great mysteries
in my heart.

165
00:06:51,333 --> 00:06:52,041
Black Emperor,

166
00:06:52,083 --> 00:06:53,083
do you think you can handle it?

167
00:06:53,958 --> 00:06:54,958
When I handle things,

168
00:06:55,083 --> 00:06:56,083
you can rest easy.

169
00:07:01,250 --> 00:07:01,832
Ye Fan,

170
00:07:02,042 --> 00:07:03,042
let me give you a hand.

171
00:07:27,042 --> 00:07:28,582
Why does it look just like me?

172
00:07:40,042 --> 00:07:41,042
Ye Fan!

173
00:07:41,083 --> 00:07:42,083
Ye Fan, what's wrong?

174
00:07:42,792 --> 00:07:43,792
Brother Ye! Ye Zi!

175
00:07:48,333 --> 00:07:49,333
Let's chase it!

176
00:07:54,625 --> 00:07:55,707
Where is this bronze coffin

177
00:07:55,708 --> 00:07:57,457
taking us anyway?

178
00:07:59,792 --> 00:08:00,291
Ye Fan,

179
00:08:00,542 --> 00:08:01,874
that's the direction
of the Desolate Ancient Forbidden Land!

180
00:08:18,542 --> 00:08:20,124
Just letting it get away like that?

181
00:08:20,875 --> 00:08:22,082
That's the Desolate Ancient Forbidden Land.

182
00:08:22,292 --> 00:08:23,292
We can't just barge in there.

183
00:08:59,292 --> 00:09:00,457
Nine Dragons pulling a coffin...

184
00:09:00,458 --> 00:09:01,082
Good heavens,

185
00:09:01,292 --> 00:09:02,374
those are real dragons!

186
00:09:02,875 --> 00:09:04,666
Such creatures actually exist?

187
00:09:04,917 --> 00:09:06,082
And there are nine of them!

188
00:09:06,625 --> 00:09:07,916
That small coffin

189
00:09:07,917 --> 00:09:09,541
could withstand the Void Mirror.

190
00:09:09,542 --> 00:09:11,207
The corpse inside the large coffin

191
00:09:11,333 --> 00:09:13,082
must be an Ancient Great Emperor.

192
00:09:13,458 --> 00:09:14,082
Otherwise,

193
00:09:14,292 --> 00:09:16,624
who else would be worthy of
having nine dragons pull their coffin?

194
00:09:39,042 --> 00:09:40,166
The Five-Colored Altar.

195
00:09:42,375 --> 00:09:43,666
It looks identical to the one

196
00:09:44,208 --> 00:09:45,208
on Mount Tai.

197
00:09:45,458 --> 00:09:46,458
Five-Colored Altar...

198
00:09:46,833 --> 00:09:47,957
Nine Dragons pulling a coffin...

199
00:09:48,917 --> 00:09:49,917
Pang Bo,

200
00:09:50,042 --> 00:09:51,082
we've finally made it.

201
00:09:52,083 --> 00:09:53,083
Black Emperor.

202
00:09:53,333 --> 00:09:54,791
How to control the altar's runes?

203
00:09:54,792 --> 00:09:56,874
How do we manipulate these glyphs?

204
00:09:56,875 --> 00:09:57,875
I don't know.

205
00:09:58,750 --> 00:09:59,999
But if it's just

206
00:10:00,250 --> 00:10:01,416
about setting coordinates...

207
00:10:03,833 --> 00:10:04,416
Speak quickly.

208
00:10:04,667 --> 00:10:06,332
It's not impossible.

209
00:10:07,375 --> 00:10:08,375
Give me a moment.

210
00:10:12,708 --> 00:10:13,708
Ten years...

211
00:10:14,958 --> 00:10:15,958
Pang Bo,

212
00:10:16,833 --> 00:10:18,082
we can finally go home.

213
00:10:18,625 --> 00:10:19,625
The moment has finally arrived.

214
00:10:21,792 --> 00:10:22,792
Ye Zi...

215
00:10:23,208 --> 00:10:24,249
This time,

216
00:10:24,250 --> 00:10:26,707
I'm afraid I cannot go with you.

217
00:10:29,625 --> 00:10:30,625
Why?

218
00:10:32,917 --> 00:10:33,917
After all these years,

219
00:10:34,750 --> 00:10:36,249
I've grown accustomed to life here.

220
00:10:37,375 --> 00:10:38,124
Besides,

221
00:10:38,125 --> 00:10:39,125
look at me now—

222
00:10:39,625 --> 00:10:41,416
my Demon Race bloodline has awakened.

223
00:10:41,625 --> 00:10:42,625
If I return to Earth,

224
00:10:42,750 --> 00:10:43,957
I'd feel out of place.

225
00:10:44,875 --> 00:10:45,875
For ten years,

226
00:10:46,375 --> 00:10:47,582
we journeyed from Earth

227
00:10:48,083 --> 00:10:49,083
to the Big Dipper.

228
00:10:49,708 --> 00:10:50,916
We endured so much,

229
00:10:50,917 --> 00:10:51,999
all for this moment.

230
00:10:52,292 --> 00:10:52,832
How can you—

231
00:10:52,958 --> 00:10:53,958
Just listen to me.

232
00:10:54,167 --> 00:10:55,749
Even if we part ways for now,

233
00:10:55,917 --> 00:10:57,541
we can both work hard.

234
00:10:58,167 --> 00:10:58,832
Let's strive to

235
00:10:58,833 --> 00:11:00,332
reconnect our two worlds soon.

236
00:11:00,458 --> 00:11:01,957
Then we can meet anytime.

237
00:11:02,417 --> 00:11:02,874
Plus,

238
00:11:02,875 --> 00:11:04,666
Ziyue and the others can visit you then.

239
00:11:04,667 --> 00:11:05,332
Kid,

240
00:11:05,583 --> 00:11:06,624
are you leaving or not?

241
00:11:07,417 --> 00:11:08,707
The key to departure

242
00:11:09,083 --> 00:11:10,707
lies within those runes.

243
00:11:11,708 --> 00:11:12,708
Those symbols must be arranged

244
00:11:12,875 --> 00:11:14,207
in sequence, placed precisely

245
00:11:14,458 --> 00:11:16,207
where they belong.

246
00:11:25,958 --> 00:11:28,916
Although the central pillar
is missing from this altar,

247
00:11:29,292 --> 00:11:31,082
it doesn't affect opening the void.

248
00:11:35,333 --> 00:11:36,166
In that case,

249
00:11:37,292 --> 00:11:38,249
I'll take my leave first.

250
00:11:39,708 --> 00:11:40,708
But remember this:

251
00:11:41,500 --> 00:11:42,666
I'll be waiting for you over there.

252
00:12:00,125 --> 00:12:01,125
This moment...

253
00:12:01,625 --> 00:12:02,625
I've waited ten years for it.

254
00:12:03,583 --> 00:12:04,583
If I miss this chance,

255
00:12:05,208 --> 00:12:06,457
I might never make it back.

256
00:12:14,375 --> 00:12:14,874
Brother Ape,

257
00:12:15,292 --> 00:12:15,832
everyone here

258
00:12:16,250 --> 00:12:17,250
is in your care now.

259
00:12:17,458 --> 00:12:18,458
Take care.

260
00:12:21,250 --> 00:12:23,707
Big Brother, where are you going?

261
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:26,207
Nannan doesn't want you to leave.

262
00:12:27,833 --> 00:12:28,833
Nannan, don't cry.

263
00:12:29,167 --> 00:12:30,791
Big Brother has to leave for a while,

264
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:32,332
to go to a very faraway place.

265
00:12:33,167 --> 00:12:34,582
Be good and listen to Brother Heishui,

266
00:12:35,042 --> 00:12:36,124
and to that black dog too.

267
00:12:39,083 --> 00:12:40,083
Black Emperor,

268
00:12:41,583 --> 00:12:42,583
as for you—

269
00:12:43,083 --> 00:12:44,541
be a proper dog.

270
00:12:44,958 --> 00:12:46,374
Stop causing trouble everywhere.

271
00:12:46,958 --> 00:12:48,166
I don't want to hear stories

272
00:12:48,583 --> 00:12:50,082
in another starfield
about how unreliable you are.

273
00:12:51,417 --> 00:12:52,417
What is your problem?

274
00:12:53,208 --> 00:12:54,582
When others say goodbye,
they're polite,

275
00:12:54,875 --> 00:12:56,082
but you just lecture me.

276
00:12:57,792 --> 00:12:58,999
Because you are...

277
00:12:59,375 --> 00:13:00,832
truly one of a kind.

278
00:13:26,667 --> 00:13:27,667
Ziyue.

279
00:13:31,625 --> 00:13:32,791
Earlier, I said I would

280
00:13:33,333 --> 00:13:35,166
travel across the Big Dipper with you,

281
00:13:35,458 --> 00:13:36,957
searching for a way home.

282
00:13:38,250 --> 00:13:39,250
I thought it would take

283
00:13:39,875 --> 00:13:41,041
a year,

284
00:13:41,458 --> 00:13:42,458
maybe two,

285
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:44,249
or even ten.

286
00:13:46,083 --> 00:13:47,291
I never expected it to happen

287
00:13:48,375 --> 00:13:49,375
so suddenly.

288
00:13:50,167 --> 00:13:51,167
Yes...

289
00:13:51,708 --> 00:13:52,708
This moment—

290
00:13:53,250 --> 00:13:54,666
I didn't expect it to be this abrupt.

291
00:13:55,542 --> 00:13:57,332
There's still so much I haven't told you.

292
00:13:58,708 --> 00:14:00,082
You once told me that

293
00:14:00,833 --> 00:14:02,749
Earth and the Big Dipper are quite different.

294
00:14:04,458 --> 00:14:06,207
But the starry river above...

295
00:14:06,833 --> 00:14:08,499
It should be the same as here, right?

296
00:14:10,625 --> 00:14:11,625
It's the same.

297
00:14:12,833 --> 00:14:15,082
If we share the same starry sky,

298
00:14:16,375 --> 00:14:17,457
then perhaps one day,

299
00:14:18,125 --> 00:14:19,707
when you truly return to Earth,

300
00:14:21,083 --> 00:14:22,582
following the customs of your world,

301
00:14:23,083 --> 00:14:24,916
we could still gaze at the same stars.

302
00:14:25,292 --> 00:14:26,292
Right?

303
00:14:28,875 --> 00:14:30,166
I will never forget

304
00:14:31,167 --> 00:14:32,457
that on the other side of the stars,

305
00:14:33,292 --> 00:14:34,707
there is a beautiful girl

306
00:14:35,625 --> 00:14:36,625
named Ziyue.

307
00:14:39,250 --> 00:14:40,291
No matter when,

308
00:14:42,458 --> 00:14:43,624
I will never forget you.

309
00:14:45,500 --> 00:14:46,957
And I won't forget you either.

310
00:14:48,042 --> 00:14:49,042
At night,

311
00:14:49,833 --> 00:14:51,624
I will look up at the starry sky,

312
00:14:52,583 --> 00:14:54,166
gazing toward the other side,

313
00:14:54,167 --> 00:14:55,291
and pray for you.

314
00:14:57,042 --> 00:14:58,416
Because I know

315
00:14:59,250 --> 00:15:00,416
you are there.

316
00:15:29,625 --> 00:15:30,625
Ye Fan.

317
00:15:34,083 --> 00:15:35,083
I can testify

318
00:15:35,292 --> 00:15:36,332
that he has absolutely

319
00:15:36,333 --> 00:15:37,333
no connection to the Ruthless One.

320
00:15:40,667 --> 00:15:41,667
Ye Fan,

321
00:15:41,708 --> 00:15:43,082
now that we are friends,

322
00:15:43,583 --> 00:15:45,791
if I ever face hardship in the future,

323
00:15:46,167 --> 00:15:47,707
you will surely rush to my aid

324
00:16:02,417 --> 00:16:03,082
without hesitation, right?

325
00:16:04,500 --> 00:16:05,500
Ziyue...

326
00:16:11,958 --> 00:16:12,958
Take care.

327
00:16:13,667 --> 00:16:14,667
I am about to embark on a long journey.

328
00:16:14,792 --> 00:16:15,957
My homeland lies
beyond the starry sea.

329
00:16:18,667 --> 00:16:20,374
Meeting all of you in this lifetime

330
00:16:21,583 --> 00:16:22,957
has been my greatest fortune.

331
00:16:25,250 --> 00:16:26,250
Farewell.

332
00:16:42,583 --> 00:16:43,583
Goodbye,

333
00:16:43,667 --> 00:16:44,667
my friends.

334
00:16:45,875 --> 00:16:47,082
Those days and nights we fought side-by-side,

335
00:16:47,375 --> 00:16:49,041
sharing life and death together,

336
00:16:49,542 --> 00:16:51,124
are forever etched in my heart.

337
00:16:52,500 --> 00:16:53,500
Farewell, Big Dipper.

338
00:16:54,417 --> 00:16:55,957
This land of crisis

339
00:16:55,958 --> 00:16:56,749
and desperate battles

340
00:16:56,750 --> 00:16:57,750
that forged my spirit.

341
00:16:57,958 --> 00:16:59,041
It was precisely these trials

342
00:16:59,375 --> 00:17:00,499
that allowed me to transform,

343
00:17:01,333 --> 00:17:02,957
rising as a true powerhouse.

344
00:17:04,542 --> 00:17:05,542
Goodbye,

345
00:17:06,042 --> 00:17:07,042
to this unforgettable chapter

346
00:17:07,833 --> 00:17:09,874
of my life.

347
00:17:30,503 --> 00:17:32,503
[Shrouding the Heavens Mini-Guide]

348
00:17:33,816 --> 00:18:09,156
[Bronze Coffin: Nine dragon corpses pull a small coffin drifting through the outer layers of the cosmos. About two meters long and less than two meters wide, it appears ancient and unremarkable. Carved with archaic patterns, its surface is covered in verdigris, bearing the weight of endless ages. Though the coffin seems heavy, it contains a primordial aura that resonates with the Dao, making it surprisingly difficult to shake. Its origins are unknown—no one knows who forged it—only that in ancient times, it set sail alongside the nine dragon corpses. Whether it belongs to this ancient history, no one can say for certain.]

349
00:18:09,180 --> 00:18:30,380
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

